le=The Italian Job |last=Travers |first=Peter |date=2003-05-30 |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2008-09-13 |archive-date=2014-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140428101227/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/the-italian-job-20030530 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

