影片的续集，暂名为《巴西任务》，于2004年夏开发，但一直面临着多方的阻力。2005年3月，主题摄影最初计划于2005年3月开始，计划于2005年11月和12月发布<ref>{{cite news | title = Sequel to ''The Italian Job'' Proposed | author = Davidson, Paul | work = IGN | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/430/430101p1.html | date = 2003-07-23 | accessdate = 2008-10-08 | archive-date = 2007-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071025070435/http://movies.ign.com/articles/430/430101p1.html | dead-url = no }} {{cite news | title = New man for the 'Job' | author = Fleming, Michael and McNary, Dave | work = Variety | publisher = Reed Business Information | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117907994.html | date = 2004-07-19 | accessdate = 2008-09-17 }} {{cite news | title = Par reunites 'Job' crew | first = Dave | last = McNary | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117910959.html | work = Variety | publisher = Reed Business Information | date = 2004-09-26 | accessdate = 2008-09-17 }} {{cite news | title = 'Huckabees' stars are all 'Heart' | author = Keck, William | work = USA Today | url = http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-09-23-huckabees-premiere_x.htm | date = 2004-09-23 | accessdate = 2008-10-10 | archive-date = 2009-08-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090822040826/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-09-23-huckabees-premiere_x.htm | dead-url = no }} See also: {{cite news | title = New Italian Job Looks Likely | first = Paul | last = Davidson | work = IGN | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/551/551886p1.html | date = 2004-09-27 | accessdate = 2008-09-17 | archive-date = 2009-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090820165528/http://movies.ign.com/articles/551/551886p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。然而，脚本迟迟未完成，发行日期被推迟到2006年<ref>{{cite news | title = Par: Déjà vu all over again | author = McNary, Dave | work = Variety | publisher = Reed Business Information | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117913091.html | date = 2004-11-07 | accessdate = 2008-10-05}} See also: {{cite news | title = Mark Wahlberg Hits The Gridiron For Role In True–Life Tale 'Invincible' | first = Brandee | last = Tecson | work = MTV | url = http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1519332/20051227/story.jhtml | date = 2005-12-27 | accessdate = 2009-03-18}}</ref>，后来改为2007年夏<ref name="Summer07">{{cite web | url = http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/676/676604p1.html | title = 'The Brazilian Job' Targets Summer 2007 | author = Davidson, Paul | date = 2005-12-16 | work = IGN | accessdate = 2008-06-17 | archive-date = 2011-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713004717/http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/676/676604p1.html | dead-url = no }} {{cite web | url = http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/785/785006p1.html | title = ''Brazilian Job'' Still On | author = Davidson, Paul | date = 2007-05-02 | work = IGN | accessdate = 2008-06-17 | archive-date = 2011-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713004724/http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/785/785006p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。编剧[[大衛·托伊|大卫·特伍]]带着《破坏能手》（The Wrecking Crew）的原创剧本接触派拉蒙影业，虽说工作室喜欢这个主意，但他们认为该作品最好是《意大利任务》的续集<ref name="Fleming">{{cite news | title = Par puts vet on the 'Job' | author = Fleming, Michael | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117923728.html | work = Variety | publisher = Reed Business Information | date = 2005-05-31 | accessdate = 2008-09-11}}</ref>。格雷再度被提名导演，但原班人马并未全数回归<ref name="Summer07" /><ref name="Fleming" />。剧本的两个草案于2007年8月写成，但该项目并未立项<ref>{{cite web | url = http://tv.ign.com/articles/813/813574p1.html | title = Exclusive Interview: Seth Green | last = Goldman | first = Eric | date = 2007-08-17 | work = IGN | accessdate = 2008-09-15 | archive-date = 2009-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090204162830/http://tv.ign.com/articles/813/813574p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2008年3月接受采访时，杰森·斯坦森表示“有人刚刚把它（电影资料）从[[IMDB|IMDB]]删除，直至前期准备完成才重新出现<ref>{{cite web | url = http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/856/856850p1.html | title = Statham Talks Sequels | author = IGN Staff | date = 2008-03-04 | work = IGN | accessdate = 2008-06-17 | archive-date = 2008-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080308230935/http://au.movies.ign.com/articles/856/856850p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。”制片人唐纳德·德·莱恩（Donald De Line）6月份透露，《巴西任务》的剧本已经开发，预算已到位，但“随着管理人员的变动发生了很多事情，剧本还是交上去了。”至于剧情，他表示将在巴西开始，设在[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]，随后转场到比利时，涉及钻石<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp/aid/8101/tcid/1 | title = Producer Donald De Line gives Updates on House of Lies, Guardians of Ga'Hoole, Green Lantern, and The Brazilian Job! | author = Weintraub, Steve | date = 2008-06-04 | work = Collider.com | accessdate = 2010-07-05 | archive-date = 2010-01-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100113035042/http://www.collider.com/entertainment/interviews/article.asp/aid/8101/tcid/1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。”然而，格林在9月表示，续集在不久的将来不太能出现<ref name="Soll">{{cite news |title=Seth Green talks 'Heroes' and 'Italian Job' sequel |author=Soll, Lindsay |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2008/09/heroes-seth.html |date=2008-09-09 |accessdate=2008-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080910013635/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2008/09/heroes-seth.html |archivedate=2008-09-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2009年3月9日，德·莱恩表示：“我们在派拉蒙非常认真地讨论了一个版本”，此外值得一提的是，剧组对项目很感兴趣<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=53545 | title = Donald De Line on 'Green Lantern' and 'Brazilian Job' | author = Douglas, Edward | date = 2009-03-09 | work = ComingSoon.net | accessdate = 2009-03-18 | archive-date = 2009-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090312023309/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=53545 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。尼尔·珀维斯和罗伯特·韦德当年一直在位续集定稿<ref>{{cite news | title = Bond begins anew with scribe trio | first = Michael | last = Fleming | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118004869.html | date = 2009-06-12 | work = Variety | publisher = Reed Business Information | accessdate = 2009-10-14}}</ref>。《[[每日纪事报|每日纪事报]]》9月报道塞隆签署了电影合同<ref>{{cite news | title = Charlize Theron: I've got no problems with the signs of aging | first = Rick | last = Fulton | url = http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-interviews/2009/09/21/charlize-theron-i-ve-got-no-problems-with-the-signs-of-aging-86908-21689417 | work = The Daily Record | date = 2009-09-21 | accessdate = 2010-04-12 | archive-date = 2009-12-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091227065017/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-interviews/2009/09/21/charlize-theron-i-ve-got-no-problems-with-the-signs-of-aging-86908-21689417/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。10月，格雷表示他享受制作《意大利任务》的过程，如果剧本定稿，他仍有担任续集导演的兴趣，认为这取决于档期<ref>{{cite news | title = Will The Brazilian Job Ever Happen? | first = Edward | last = Douglas | url = http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=59774 | work = ComingSoon.net | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2009-10-12 | archive-date = 2009-10-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091008085452/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=59774 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2010年1月，特伍接受采访时表示：“《巴西任务》可能不会有。我几年前就寫了剧本，他们在IMDB上不断折腾它。派拉蒙——我还能说什么<ref>{{cite web | url = http://thefilmstage.com/2010/01/18/exclusive-david-twohy-talks-riddick-3-and-the-brazilian-job | title = [Exclusive] David Twohy Talks Riddick 3 And The Brazilian Job | last = Giroux | first = Jack | date = 2010-01-18 | work = The Film Stage | accessdate = 2010-07-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100720002358/http://thefilmstage.com/2010/01/18/exclusive-david-twohy-talks-riddick-3-and-the-brazilian-job/ | archivedate = 2010-07-20 }}</ref>？”6月份，当被问及续集时，格林表示“《巴西任务》实际上不存在”，并将其称为“IMDB的精彩神话<ref>{{cite web | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/110/1101504p1.html | title = The Brazilian Job Is a No Go | last = Lieberman | first = Jason | date = 2010-06-30 | work = IGN | accessdate = 2010-07-05 | archive-date = 2010-07-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100705004017/http://movies.ign.com/articles/110/1101504p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>”。

